    {
      "id": "56f36314_37b9bc7b",
      "file_path": "docs/Chapter8/ves_7_2/ves_event_listener_7_2.rst",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 3502,
      "message": "Well, this is following OMA: https://www.openmobilealliance.org/release/REST_NetAPI_Common/V1_0-20180116-A/OMA-TS-REST_NetAPI_Common-V1_0-20180116-A.pdf\n\nThere is a Text defined, with variables.\nI used here the text values for variables, as we might use the same text to express issues related to other variables, e.g. schemaReference, data,...\n\nSo there are really variables in the text, which can change, depending, on where we have this issue in the event received.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 5597,
        "name": "Damian Nowak",
        "display_name": "Damian Nowak",
        "email": "damian.nowak@nokia.com",
        "username": "deen1985"
      },
      "updated": "2020-06-29 14:53:07.000000000",
